Prepare Repo:

  $ newclientrepo repo
  $ setconfig paths.default=test:e1
  $ drawdag << 'EOS'
  > E
  > |
  > D
  > |
  > C
  > |
  > B
  > |
  > A
  > EOS

  $ hg push -r $E --to master --create -q

